SizePolicy:

sizeHint(期望尺寸)：sizeHint对于大多数的控件来说都是只读的；

读取期望尺寸：
单位是pixel
self.textEdit.sizeHint().width()
self.textEdit.sizeHint().height()
print("The textEdit SizeHint width  is ",self.textEdit.sizeHint().width(), "pixel")
print("The textEdit SizeHint height is ",self.textEdit.sizeHint().height(), "pixel")

最小的期望尺寸：

self.textEdit.minimumSizeHint().width()
self.textEdit.minimumSizeHint().height()